data.description:
Join us for an Engineering career happy hour event hosted by SignalFire, featuring special guest Alan Shreve, Founder of Ngrok, a tool used by millions of developers every day.
In this event, Alan will share his engineering career milestones and talk about his experience bootstrapping and transitioning from full-time engineer to CEO. Attendees will have the opportunity to engage in discussions, ask questions, and network with other engineers in a casual setting.
This event aims to provide valuable insights and strategies for engineers at various stages of their careers who are looking to advance their professional growth and explore new opportunities.
data.event_name: Engineering Career Happy Hour feat. ngrok creator Alan Shreve
